|               |                         TableScan: orders projection=[o_orderkey, o_custkey]                                                                                                                                                                                                        |
|               |                     TableScan: customer projection=[c_custkey, c_nationkey]                                                                                                                                                                                                         |
|               |                 SubqueryAlias: n1                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   |
|               |                   Filter: nation.n_name = Utf8("FRANCE") OR nation.n_name = Utf8("GERMANY")                                                                                                                                                                                         |
