|               |             SubqueryAlias: n2                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       |
|               |               Filter: nation.n_name = Utf8("GERMANY") OR nation.n_name = Utf8("FRANCE")                                                                                                                                                                                             |
|               |                 TableScan: nation projection=[n_nationkey, n_name]                                                                                                                                                                                                                  |
